Sentencas: A one-step process has been developed for the fabrication of thin film membrane-electrode assemblies with multi-layer electrolytes for use in high-performance, low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (LT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Single-chamber fabrication of high-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with grain-controlled functional layers

Sentencas: By controlling the sputter processing conditions, a dense yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film was fabricated onto a porous aluminum oxide (AAO) anodic substrate.
Titulo: Single-chamber fabrication of high-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with grain-controlled functional layers

Sentencas: Thin, grain-controlled layers (GCLs) were subsequently formed at the cathodic interface to provide a homogeneous functional layer, which significantly enhanced the kinetics of the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR).
Titulo: Single-chamber fabrication of high-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with grain-controlled functional layers

Sentencas: This is attributed to the fine grains and increased grain boundary density of this layer, which were achieved without thermal annealing.
Titulo: Single-chamber fabrication of high-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with grain-controlled functional layers

Sentencas: Using this new device architecture, the fuel cell was able to reach a peak power density of 343 mW cm(-2) at 450 degrees C.
Titulo: Single-chamber fabrication of high-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells with grain-controlled functional layers
